Early Access Review

Maybe I am too lucky or not, but I didn't play original FTL game which is frequently quoted in other reviews and articles about Space Rogue, so I would like to express my opinion in more simple way:

Positive:
- good detailed tutorial which is directly integrated into gameplay;
- catchy graphics;
- I didn't notice any major bugs at the moment (!).

Negative:
- the player is thrown into full fight with enemy captain with an ability to lose from the start and without autosave after tutorial, so that irritates when you didn't understand quickly some things during tutorial (that's my case), so I guess that developers should consider the pacing from the start of the game and give more options to beginners or at least balance the first fight in such way that you can't lose it;
- combination of 2D animations after long fight with enemy in 3D/isometric space gives weird feelings, really.
